{"title_page": "Opinion polling for the 2023 Turkish general election", "text_new": "In the run up to the [[2023 Turkish general election|Turkish general election]] scheduled to take place in 2023, various organisations carry out [[opinion polling]] to gauge voting intention in [[Turkey]]. Results of such polls are displayed in this article. These polls only include Turkish voters nationwide and do not take into account [[Turkish diaspora|Turkish expatriates]] voting abroad. The date range for these opinion polls are from the [[2018 Turkish general election|previous general election]], held on 24 June 2018, to the present day.\n\n==Presidential election==\n\n===First round===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%; line-height:17px;\"\n|- style=\"height:42px; background:#e9e9e9;\"\n! class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"3\"| Date\n! class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"3\"| Polling firm\n! class=\"unsortable\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Justice and Development Party (Turkey)|AKP]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" colspan=\"3\"| [[Republican People's Party (Turkey)|CHP]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" colspan=\"2\"| [[Peoples' Democratic Party (Turkey)|HDP]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" colspan=\"2\"| [[\u0130Y\u0130 Party|\u0130Y\u0130]]\n![[Nationalist Movement Party|MHP]]\n![[Future Party (Turkey)|GP]]\n![[Democracy and Progress Party|DEVA]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"2\"| Others\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:40px;\" rowspan=\"3\"| Lead\n|-\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Generic\n! class=\"unsortable\"| [[Recep Tayyip Erdo\u011fan|Erdo\u011fan]]\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Generic\n! class=\"unsortable\"| [[Muharrem \u0130nce|\u0130nce]]\n! class=\"unsortable\"| [[Ekrem \u0130mamo\u011flu|\u0130mamo\u011flu]]\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Generic\n! class=\"unsortable\"| [[Selahattin Demirta\u015f|Demirta\u015f]]\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Generic\n! class=\"unsortable\"| [[Meral Ak\u015fener|Ak\u015fener]]\n! class=\"unsortable\"| [[Devlet Bah\u00e7eli|Bah\u00e7eli]]\n! cl