rvey is displayed in bold, and the background shaded in the leading party's color. In the instance that there is a tie, then no figure is shaded. The lead column on the right shows the percentage-point difference between the two parties with the highest figures. When a specific poll does not show a data figure for a party, the party's cell corresponding to that poll is shown empty.\n\n===Graphical summary===\n[[File:Turkish polls 2023.png|1000px]]\n\n===Party vote===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%; line-height:17px;\"\n|- style=\"height:42px; background:#e9e9e9;\"\n!class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"2\"| Date\n!class=\"unsortable\" rowspan=\"2\"| Polling firm\n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[Justice and Development Party (Turkey)|AKP]]\n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[Republican People's Party (Turkey)|CHP]]\n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[Peoples' Democratic Party (Turkey)|HDP]]\n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[\u0130Y\u0130 Party|\u0130Y\u0130]] \n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[Nationalist Movement Party|MHP]]\n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[Felicity Party|SP]]\n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[Future Party (Turkey)|GP]]\n!class=\"unsortable\"| [[Democracy and Progress Party|DEVA]]\n!class=\"unsortable\"| Others\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:40px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Lead\n|-\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:{{Justice and Development Party (Turkey)/meta/color}}; width:40px;\" |\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:{{Republican People's Party (Turkey)/meta/color}}; width:40px;\"|\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:{{Peoples' Democratic Party (Turkey)/meta/color}}; width:40px;\"|\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:{{\u0130Y\u0130 Party/meta/color}}; width:40px;\" |\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:{{Nationalist Movement Party/meta/color}}; width:40px;\"|\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:{{Felicity Party/meta/color}}; width:40px;\"|\n!class=\"unsortable\" style=\"background:{{Future Party (Turkey)/meta/color}}; width:40px;\"