cade\n| length17 = 2:43\n| all_writing = \n| total_length = \n}}\n{{tracklist\n| headline     = Banda Sonora Original (Disc 2)\n| extra_column = Performer(s)\n| collapsed    = yes\n|title1         = Will He Shoemaker?\n|writer1        =\n|extra1         =\n|length1        = 3:19\n|title2         = Shrine and Dash\n|writer2        =\n|extra2         =\n|length2        = 1:24\n|title3         = Miguel's Got an Axe to Find\n|writer3        =\n|extra3         =\n|length3        = 1:18\n|title4         = The Strum of Destiny\n|writer4        =\n|extra4         =\n|length4        = 1:11\n|title5         = It's All Relative\n|writer5        =\n|extra5         =\n|length5        = 2:38\n|title6         = Crossing the Marigold Bridge\n|writer6        =\n|extra6         =\n|length6        = 1:49\n|title7         = Dept. of Family Reunions\n|writer7        =\n|extra7         =\n|length7        = 2:46\n|title8         = The Skeleton Key to Escape\n|writer8        =\n|extra8         =\n|length8        = 3:04\n|title9         = The Newbie Skeleton Walk\n|writer9        =\n|extra9         =\n|length9        = 1:09\n|title10         = Adi\u00f3s Chicharr\u00f3n\n|writer10        =\n|extra10         =\n|length10        = 1:45\n|title11         = Plaza de la Cruz\n|writer11        =\n|extra11         =\n|length11        = 0:22\n|title12         = Family Doubtings\n|writer12        =\n|extra12         =\n|length12        = 2:25\n|title13         = Taking Sides\n|writer13        =\n|extra13         =\n|length13        = 0:57\n|title14         = Fiesta Espectacular\n|writer14        =\n|extra14         =\n|length14        = 0:57\n|title15         = Fiesta con de la Cruz\n|writer15        =\n|extra15         =\n|length15        = 2:34\n|title16         = I Have a Great-Great-Grandson\n|writer16        =\n|extra16         =\n|length16        = 1:15\n|title17         = A Blessing and a Fessing\n|writer17        =\n|extra17         =\n|length17        = 4:46\n|title18         = Cave Dwellin