 Loco\n|writer4         = Franco & Molina\n|extra4          = Joao Pedro Gon\u00e7alves & Leit\u00e3o\n|length4         = 1:52\n|title5          = J\u00e1lale (Instrumental)\n|writer5         = Holger Beier, Pat Beier, & [[Camilo Lara]]\n|extra5          = [[Mexican Institute of Sound]]\n|length5         = 2:54\n|title6          = O Mundo es Mi Fam\u00edlia\n|writer6         = Franco & Molina\n|extra6          = Gon\u00e7alves & Redondo\n|length6         = 0:50\n|title7          = Lembra-te de Mim (Can\u00e7\u00e3o de Embalar)\n|writer7         = Anderson-Lopez & Lopez\n|extra7          = Leit\u00e3o & Maria Galante\n|length7         = 1:09\n|title8          = [[La Llorona (song)|La Llorona]]\n|writer8         = Traditional\n|extra8          = [[Alanna Ubach]] & Antonio Sol\n|length8         = 2:45\n|title9          = Lembra-te de Mim (Reuni\u00e3o)\n|writer9         = Anderson-Lopez & Lopez\n|extra9          = Gon\u00e7alves & Ermelinda Duarte\n|length9         = 1:13\n|title10         = Pulsar do Meu Coraz\u00f3n\n|writer10        = Franco & Molina\n|extra10         = Gon\u00e7alves\n|length10        = 2:03\n|title11         = Remember Me (D\u00fao)\n|writer11        = Anderson-Lopez & Lopez\n|extra11         = [[Natalia Lafourcade]] & [[Miguel (singer)|Miguel]]\n|length11        = 2:44\n|title12         = Will He Shoemaker?\n|writer12        =\n|extra12         =\n|length12        = 3:19\n|title13         = Shrine and Dash\n|writer13        =\n|extra13         =\n|length13        = 1:24\n|title14         = Miguel's Got an Axe to Find\n|writer14        =\n|extra14         =\n|length14        = 1:18\n|title15         = The Strum of Destiny\n|writer15        =\n|extra15         =\n|length15        = 1:11\n|title16         = It's All Relative\n|writer16        =\n|extra16         =\n|length16        = 2:38\n|title17         = Crossing the Marigold Bridge\n|writer17        =\n|extra17         =\n|length17        = 1:49\n|title18         = Dept. of Family Reunions\n|wr