m Festival Award for Best Float|Best Float]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''Odyssey Flores - ''[[Thy Womb]]'''''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''[[El Presidente (film)|El Presidente]]'''''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival Award for Most Gender-Sensitive Film|Most Gender- Sensitivity Film]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Gatpuno Antonio J. Villegas Cultural Awards]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''[[Thy Womb]]'' - Centerstage Productions'''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''[[Thy Womb]]'' - Centerstage Productions'''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Fernando Poe Jr. Memorial Award for Excellence]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''[[One More Try (film)|One More Try]]'' - [[Star Cinema]]'''\n|}\n\n===New Wave category===\n{| class=wikitable style=\"width=\"150%\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Best ''New Wave'' Full-Length Film]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Special Jury Prize]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''The Grave Bandits'' - Tyrone Acierto'''''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''Ad Ignorantiam'' - Quantum Films'''''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Best ''New Wave'' Actor]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Best ''New Wave'' Actress]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''Allan Paule - ''Gayak'''''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''Liza Dino - ''In Nomine Matris'''''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Gender Sensitivity Award]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Best ''New Wave'' Director Award]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''In Nomine Matris'' - Mr. Will Fredo'''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''Tyrone Ancierto - ''The Grave Bandits'''''\n|-\n! colspan=2 style=\"background:#EEDD82;\"| Short Film Category\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Best Student's Short Film Award]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Most Gender Sensitive Award]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''Pukpok'' - [[De La Salle University]]'''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n*'''''Manibela - ''[[Far Eastern University]]'''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Special Jury Prize]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''Tagad'' - [[University of San Carlos]]'''\n|}\n\n===1st CinePhone Film Festival===\n{| class=wikitable style=\"width=\"150%\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Luzon]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Visayas]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''Monthsary'' - [[Polytechnic University of the Philippines]]'''\n* '''''Promdi'' - Don Bosco Youth Center'''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''Two Minutes'' - [[University of San Carlos]]'''\n* '''''License to Drive'' - Christian Academy of Bacolod'''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\" ! style=\"width=\"50%\" | [[Metro Manila Film Festival New Wave Awards|Mindanao]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n* '''''The Boy, the Girl and the Traffic Man'' - [[Ateneo de Davao University]]'''\n* '''''Bulgaran sa Daan'' - Philippine Nikkei Jin Kai International High School'''\n|}\n\n===Special awards===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" rowspan=2 width=45% border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" background: #f6e39c;\n|- style=\"background:#bebebe;\"\n|-\n|'''[[Metro Manila Film Festival Special Awards|Youth Choice Award for Best Film]]'''||[[El Presidente (film)|El Presidente]]\n|-\n|'''[[Metro Manila Film Fes